item.title: Pinisi Sinar Puupi Ship Body
item.description: How to Make a Pinisi Boat Pinisi Boat is made using teak and mahogany wood. Teak and mahogany wood are collected every 5th and the 7th of every month (the 5th has the meaning of sustenance that is already in hand and the 7th means always to get a fortune).
